extendedInfo.description: You want to learn different alphabets ? Latin, Arabic, Hebrew, Russian, Greek and even the geeky one : Elfic ?Download Alphabet Challenge !Warning : This is a game ;)The most addicting "touch the letters" game.- You can choose from different alphabet : (Latin, Arabic, Hebrew, Russian, Greek and ... Elfic :)) - More to come and we are waiting for your proposals.- Challenge your friends on your preferred alphabet - Learn new alphabets (also funny ones)- Be the faster and submit your scores in the "Online Alphabet Challenge"

reviews.title: Simple Match-To-Sample Only
reviews.comment: I was expecting some relation between the letters (match a given capital letter to it\'s miniscule, etc.) to be matched; this doesn\'t help learn anything, it\'s just finding the same shapes.
